							<img src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/86A8787-100x100.jpg" width="96" height="96" srcset="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/86A8787-300x300.jpg 2x" alt="Jonathan Lethem" class="avatar avatar-96 wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-96 alignnone photo" />						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="bio">
						<h4>Jonathan Lethem</h4>
												<p>Jonathan Lethem is the bestselling author of twelve novels, including <Em>The Arrest, The Feral Detective, The Fortress of Solitude,</em> and <em>Motherless Brooklyn</em>, winner of the National Book Critics Circle Award. He currently teaches creative writing at Pomona College in California.</p>
					</div>
